                                         "text":  "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgMath12\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMath12', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>F i g u r a 1</b>: N e s t a   f i g u r a ,   a s   c o o r d e n a d a s   g e o g r á f i c a s   s ã o   u t i l i z a d a s   p a r a   l o c a l i z a r   u m   p o n t o   n a   e s f e r a</p>",
